{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Roasted Chicken with Orange Spice","content":["Preheat oven to 200°C. Place chicken thighs in a deep oven proof dish then set aside.","Place garlic, coriander, oregano, cumin, salt and orange juice in mixing bowl then grind <b>10 sec\/speed 8<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then grind again <b>5 sec\/speed 10<b>. Add to oven-proof dish and rub into chicken thighs then top each thigh with a slice of orange. Scatter over green olives then cover dish with aluminium foil.","Bake for 60 minutes (200°C) until cooked through, removing foil for last 15 minutes to brown chicken. After 35 minutes, prepare rice."]},{"title":"Basmati Rice","content":["Place onions, carrots and olive oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then sauté <b>5 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place water and salt in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in rice, raisins and onion mixture. Mix well with spatula and rinse <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b> then steam <b>16 min\/100°C\/speed 4<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and transfer rice to a serving dish.","Serve cooked chicken with rice, sprinkled with toasted flaked almonds."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Roasted Chicken with Orange Spice","content":["6 - 8 chicken thighs, skin on, large (approx. 200 g each)","3 - 4 garlic cloves, to taste","1 Tbsp coriander seeds","1 Tbsp dried oregano","1 tsp ground cumin","1 tsp fine sea salt","30 g orange juice","1 orange, sliced (5 mm)","70 g green olives, pitted"]},{"title":"Basmati Rice","content":["100 g onions, cut in pieces","150 g carrots, cut in pieces","20 g olive oil","1000 g water","1 tsp fine sea salt","300 g basmati rice","50 g raisins","1 Tbsp flaked almonds, toasted"]}],"id":"r140979","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GujQZr1_VC4\/XZQv5ZiEL6I\/AAAAAAAAcg4\/BSH1FjKzu90a3J7G8rfHuRliDYTrDCQiACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_PcOULkwIEshNtJ-_.png","title":"Orange Roasted Chicken Thighs with Basmati Rice","publishedAt":"2017-01-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"42.1 g","fat":"42.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"53.9 g","calories":"3214 kJ \/ 768 kcal"},"usefulItems":"oven-proof dish, aluminium foil, serving dish, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Swap chicken for your favourite vegetarian alternative."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","6 portions"]}